# Tactical Ops Rework — Strip Minigames, Keep Effects

Replace Breach Protocol puzzles, stamina races, mission board slots, and 1v1 duels with a **fund → launch → effect** system.

---

## Two Tiers of Operations

| | Country Ops (President launches) | Player Ops (Solo) |
|---|---|---|
| **Who funds** | Any citizen via micro-missions | Player pays directly |
| **Who launches** | President only (once funded) | Any player |
| **Ops** | Company Sabotage, Logistics Disruption, Power Grid Attack, Air Strike, Naval Strike | Resource Intel, War Intel, Disinformation, Bunker Override |
| **Base success** | 60% + research bonus | 60% + research bonus |

