## Bunker Override — Whale Op

> [!CAUTION]
> Bunker Override costs **20 ₿ + 20 🎖️** — the ultimate pre-attack softener for wealthy players.

Effect: Halves enemy bunker defense for 24 hours. Meant to be launched right before a major coordinated attack.

