## Casual Micro-Missions (Country Op Funding)

Each Country Op needs **15 funding points** before the president can launch. Missions:

| Mission | Cost | Points | Who can do it |
|---|---|---|---|
| 🔧 Supply Run | 10 work energy | +1 | Anyone |
| 💧 Field Support | 20 stamina | +1 | Anyone |
| 🎖️ Pledge Badge | 1 Badge of Honor | +2 | Anyone |
| ₿ War Bonds | 1 Bitcoin | +3 | Economy players |
| ⚔️ Battle Veteran | Deal 500+ dmg in any battle | +2 | Combat players |

